    "We then use LSI to evaluate ChatGPT and GPT-4 for bias across four demographics: nationality, gender, race, and religion.",
    "We share some critical insights from our large-scale experiments with 157k generations that we believe are quite concerning.",
    "As there are many more research insights to be drawn from these experiments and data, we are releasing all the code and data publicly. foot_0",
